<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
    <!-- The head tag contains all the meta elements containing metadata about the page, along with links to other assets such as the style
    sheet css, also includes the main title of the page. -->
    <head>
        <meta charset="utf-8">
        <meta name="description" content="About the restaurant">        
        <meta name="keywords" content="Town, Chinese cuisine, variety, vision, vision statement, about us">
        <meta name="author" content="Kevin Caballero">       
        <meta name="viewport" content="width = device-width, initial-scale=1">        
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="css/stylesheet.css"> 
        <title>About us</title>
        <!-- This style section contains the design elements that are associated with the dominant image that aligns the vision statement to the right of the image. -->
        <style>
        /*About page image alignment with text*/
        .container{
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;           
        }
        .imagecontainer{
            margin-right: 8px;
        }
        .aboutimage{
            margin: 24px auto;
            width: 100%;
            height: auto;
            border: 4px solid #be1e2d50;
            border-radius: 10px;
        } 
        .visionheader{
            font-family: majesti_bannerbold;
            font-size: 42px;
            color: #d4a18d;
        }
        .visionstate{
            text-align: center;
            font-family: 'majesti_bannermedium';        
            font-size: 24px;
            padding: 5% 5%;
            margin: auto;
            color: white;
            border-bottom: 50px solid #be1e2d50;
            border-top: 50px solid #be1e2d50;
        }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        {{> header}}
        <div class="container">
            <div class="imagecontainer">
                <!-- Dominant about-us image -->
                <Img class="aboutimage" src="images/plates.jpg" alt="Individual with chopsticks reaching for chinese food on a platter">
            </div>      
            <div class="visionstate">
                <!-- Vision statement header -->
                <h1 class="visionheader">Vision</h1>
                <!-- Vision Statement paragraphs -->
                <p>TOWN combines a variety of chinese cuisine
                    to excite and delight our customers.</p>
                <p>Our vision for the future is to create
                    experiential dining that is more than just
                    a night out. We aim to bring quality and
                    luxury across all aspects of our brand.</p>
                <p>The approach of TOWN is to develop our
                    brand with the understanding of both our
                    culture and consumer insights. Within our
                    vision always lives the promise of inspiring
                    creativity, conversation and quality. </p>
                <p>Our audience is a high-end clientele who
                    values a dining experience. The age range
                    of our customers are from early 30s-60s.
                    We would like them to come back for both
                    personal dining and events.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
        <!-- Contains the footer info. for each page listing the location, hours, email, as well as phone number of the restaurant. -->
        {{> footer}}     
    </body>
</html>